# ============================================
# UE5 蓝图日志自动化工具链 — .gitignore
# 将本文件复制到你的 UE 项目根目录使用
# ============================================

# === 密钥与凭据（绝对不能提交）===
.env
*.env
*.env.local
*.env.*.local
secrets/
credentials.json
service-account.json

# === Python ===
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.venv/
venv/
env/

# === IDE ===
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# === OS ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === UE5 生成文件（由工具链导出）===
# 蓝图拓扑 JSON — 包含核心业务逻辑，绝对不能提交！
ue_blueprint_status.json
Saved/BlueprintTopology/
Intermediate/
DerivedDataCache/

# === 笔记（按需决定是否提交）===
# UENoteBook/ — 开发笔记，包含设计思考，建议提交
# Review_Docs/ — AI 审阅报告，建议提交
